'From Squeak3.1alpha of 4 February 2001 [latest update: #3682] on 20 February 2001 at 10:26:11 pm'!"Change Set:		NoSound-arDate:			20 February 2001Author:			Andreas RaabDon't bother playing a sound that has no samples left. Happens quite a bit for this very special sound named 'silence' and leads to spurious attempts of starting the sound player."!!SoundPlayer class methodsFor: 'playing' stamp: 'ar 2/19/2001 01:28'!playSound: aSound	"Reset and start playing the given sound from its beginning."	aSound reset.	aSound samplesRemaining = 0 ifTrue:[^self].	self resumePlaying: aSound.! !